query:
SELECT
                sale_items.product_name AS "name_at_sale",
                sale_items.price_at_sale,
                sale_items.quantity,
                products.id AS "product_id: uuid::Uuid",
                products.category,
                products.name,
                products.price,
                products.is_deleted AS 'is_product_deleted'
            FROM sale_items
                JOIN products ON sale_items.product_id = products.id
            WHERE sale_id = ?
